# Do Not Modify Backend

- **Never edit, add, or delete files under** `app/` (Laravel backend: controllers, models, etc.), `routes/`, `database/`, or any PHP backend code in this project.
- All changes must be frontend-only (e.g. `resources/js/`, Blade/Inertia views) unless the user explicitly asks to change the backend.
- In chat, do not give backend advice; only describe frontend work (see rule `frontend-only-discussion.mdc`).
